wikipedia_page.main: Nicosia Lawson is a beauty queen who represented the Cayman Islands in both Miss World 2008 and Miss Universe 2009. She previously placed 2nd runner-up in the 2000 Miss Teen Cayman Islands competition.

response: In August 2008 she passed on her Miss Cayman Islands crown to Nicosia Lawson.(24 August 2008) Miss Cayman crowned, Cay Compass, Retrieved October 26, 2010
